0px" /></p><p> Michael Kiwanuka、Bad Gyal、Alice Phoebe Lou、Amyl And The Sniffer 和 English Teacher 等人将在西班牙音乐节上演出</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pulp-kylie-minogue-raye-lead-bilbao-bbk-2025-line-up-3818849">Pulp、Kylie Minogue、RAYE 领衔的毕尔巴鄂 BBK 2025 阵容</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Jarvis-Cocker-of-Pulp-Kylie-Minogue-and-RAYE.-CREDIT_-Samir-Hussein_WireImage-Joseph-Okpako_WireImage-and-Dominic-Lipinski_Getty-Images-for-Paramount.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Jarvis-Cocker-of-Pulp-Kylie-Minogue-and-RAYE.-CREDIT_-Samir-Hussein_WireImage-Joseph-Okpako_WireImage-and-Dominic-Lipinski_Getty-Images-for-Paramount.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Jarvis-Cocker-of-Pulp-Kylie-Minogue-and-RAYE.-CREDIT_-Samir-Hussein_WireImage-Joseph-Okpako_WireImage-and-Dominic-Lipinski_Getty-Images-for-Paramount-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Jarvis-Cocker-of-Pulp-Kylie-Minogue-and-RAYE.-CREDIT_-Samir-Hussein_WireImage-Joseph-Okpako_WireImage-and-Dominic-Lipinski_Getty-Images-for-Paramount-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Jarvis-Cocker-of-Pulp-Kylie-Minogue-and-RAYE.-CREDIT_-Samir-Hussein_WireImage-Joseph-Okpako_WireImage-and-Dominic-Lipinski_Getty-Images-for-Paramount-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Jarvis-Cocker-of-Pulp-Kylie-Minogue-and-RAYE.-CREDIT_-Samir-Hussein_WireImage-Joseph-Okpako_WireImage-and-Dominic-Lipinski_Getty-Images-for-Paramount-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Jarvis-Cocker-of-Pulp-Kylie-Minogue-and-RAYE.-CREDIT_-Samir-Hussein_WireImage-Joseph-Okpako_WireImage-and-Dominic-Lipinski_Getty-Images-for-Paramount-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Bilbao BKK 公布了 2025 年阵容的第一波表演，其中包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pulp">Pulp</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kylie-minogue">Kylie Minogue</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/raye">RAYE</a> 。查看下面的更多名称。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/festivals-blog/bilbao-bbk-live-2023-review-arctic-monkeys-pavement-bring-magic-to-the-basque-mountains-3467026">毕尔巴鄂 BBK Live 2023：北极猴子和人行道为巴斯克山脉带来魔力</a></strong></li></ul><p>2025 年版定于 7 月 10 日至 12 日在毕尔巴鄂科塔门迪拉开帷幕， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/michael-kiwanuka">Michael Kiwanuka</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nathy-peluso">Nathy Peluso</a>和 Bad Gyal 也将登台表演。</p><p>周末其他地方还将有<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/alice-phoebe-lou">Alice Phoebe Lou</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/amyl-and-the-sniffers">Amyl And The Sniffers</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jalen-ngonda">Jalen Ngonda</a> 、Jessica Pratt、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/english-teacher">English Teacher</a> 、L&#39;impératrice、Makaya McCraven、Obongjayar、Sofie Royer、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/wunderhorse">Wunderhorse</a>等乐队的表演。</p><p>一般门票销售将于欧洲中部时间下周三（12 月 11 日）中午 12 点开始，并可<a href="http://bilbaobbklive.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>购买。另外，之前的与会者也可以参加周四（12 月 5 日）上午 10 点开始的预售。</p><p>查看下面已确认行为的完整列表。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DDJ2_7wi6U3/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style